====== H5039: נְבָלָה ======

===== Source =====

feminine of  H5036 ;

===== Meaning =====

foolishness , i.e. (morally)  wickedness ; concretely, a  crime ; by extension,  punishment

===== Definitions =====

  - foolishness
  - wickedness
  - crime
  - punishment

===== Usage =====

folly, vile, villany.
